summary: I think there will be more shows with the cast later. Emilia and Kit are definitely will be everywhere. I want Sophie to attend...
question: I think there will be more shows with the cast later. Emilia and Kit are definitely will be everywhere. I want Sophie to attend something too, she's always ignored.
answer:
Hi !

Maybe later ! That’s a possibility. Not only in USA, I hope. There are talk shows in UK (Sophie, Maisie, Emilia, Kit, Lena & Isaac are british after all) etc. We will see. Plus they all did an interview in May last year. I guess they’ll release it in April 🤷‍♀️

I was hoping they’ll do more promo for the last season. GoT is the most popular show from the last years. That makes sense to me.

summary: The only reason Arya stans think Maisie Williams doesn’t understand Arya is because Maisie doesn’t hate Sansa. She gave an...
body:
The only reason Arya stans think Maisie Williams doesn’t understand Arya is because Maisie doesn’t hate Sansa. She gave an interview last year about Arya behaving horribly towards Sansa (which is accurate) and they turned on her like they’re turning on her now. Arya stans hate Sansa almost as much as they love Arya and they’re willing to throw the actress playing their faves under the bus for having an opinion.

The real Sansa fandom has a lot of issues and we disagree with Sophie on several topics but we’d never treat her the way Maisie is being treated.
